{"tid":2298840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自由黨：確診獎金加多$4000，令總津貼為$9000 名額5百個 先到先得","createTime":"2020-11-24T10:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T17:12:50.000Z","uid":22556,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dbe9cd85b51eb99a9a3030c1e24c6f37d7d2e9d6","tid":2298840,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"自由黨表示，支持政府為沒有薪病假受僱或自僱的確診患者，派發一筆過5000元的津貼，並會啟動該黨的「關懷基金」，撥出200萬元，為合資格得到政府津貼的航運交通業、飲食業、零售及批發界、紡織及製衣業界的從業員再提供4000元補貼，名額暫定為500名，不排除會籌集更多資金，讓更多人受惠。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561659-20201124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561659-20201124.htm&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=157a5983\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561659-20201124.htm&h=13f7e49a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561659-20201124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e53107d4de72006d47de3b3b4b55386bea32a940","tid":2298840,"uid":74361,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"IT界加多50蚊ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b377bd293acace4c15e49b3f2100e755a76d11ee","tid":2298840,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17dbee253cb4177d55fa339bbbdea6c509ba5723","tid":2298840,"uid":15010,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"名額暫定為500名<br />\n<br />\n先中先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fdbf9854d8122cb4fb36525484d029e7f31286","tid":2298840,"uid":30145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"